org.semanticweb.rulewerk.parser.javacc

Class JavaCCParserBase

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.semanticweb.rulewerk.parser.javacc.JavaCCParserBase
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    JavaCCParser

    public class JavaCCParserBase
extends Object
    Basic methods used in the JavaCC-generated parser. Implementation of some string escaping methods adapted from Apache Jena, released under Apache 2.0 license terms.
    Author:
    Markus Kroetzsch, Larry Gonzalez, Maximilian Marx, Jena developers, Apache Software Foundation (ASF)
    See Also:
    https://github.com/apache/jena/blob/master/jena-core/src/main/java/org/apache/jena/n3/turtle/ParserBase.java
